[Fixed Impossible Camping Spots]
[Added Some Secrets to help both teams]
[Added more props and changed some props]

About the map:
The map is decently big and is based on the house. It has a first floor,second,basement,garage,pool and a cellar. The garage has a nice hiding spot in the attic as well as the basement. Their are some secrets that will help benefit humans such as breakable stuff...aka closets,doors.

Well Enough Said and Go play!



Time of setting:Night with some scary sounds added to the map
